OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFine and largely sunny, with
OL,6,Fany overnight cloud soon clearing.
OL,7,FSunshine could be hazy at times, or
OL,8,Finterrupted by some high cloud,
OL,9,Fhowever it will be another very warm
OL,10,Fday with light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry evening with clear skies
OL,13,Ffor many, but also the odd patch of
OL,14,Fhigher cloud, perhaps thickest in the
OL,15,Feast. Staying dry overnight with light
OL,16,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
