OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FAnother very warm, dry and
OL,6,Flargely sunny day, with just
OL,7,Foccasional interruptions from higher
OL,8,Fcloud, most likely later in the day.
OL,9,FTurning breezy especially along the
OL,10,FEnglish Channel coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCooler
OL,13,Fwith sunny spells and showers Sunday,
OL,14,Fthese perhaps heavy at times. Dry
OL,15,FMonday, with lighter winds, variable
OL,16,Fcloud and sunny periods. Warm and
OL,17,Fsunny again Tuesday with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
